                      on November 27, 2006 at 9:45am EST
        </li>
        
                <li class="comment-body">
          
<p>As a former student at TESC I can state without reservation that Mr. Olander is one of the most inspiring educators on This Dying Earth. The cruise sounds like more fun than Showboat World.</p>        </li>
              </ul>
    
